title: String

properties.name: description
properties.value: String might refer to any of the following:

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:String

String might refer to any of the following:

  • Bow string, an item created by using flax with a spinning wheel, and used in Fletching to make bows
  • Crossbow string, an item created by using sinew with a spinning wheel, and used in Fletching to make crossbows
  • Magic string, an item created by using Magic tree roots with a spinning wheel, and used in Crafting to create Nature amulets
  • String Jewellery, a Magic spell in the Lunar spellbook that turns all unstrung amulets in the player's inventory into strung amulets
  • Ball of wool, an item used in Crafting to turn an unstrung amulet into a strung amulet, and which may also be known as a ball of string
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.

*[[String Jewellery]], a Magic spell in the [[Lunar spellbook]] that turns all unstrung amulets in the player's inventory into strung amulets
*[[Ball of wool]], an item used in Crafting to turn an unstrung amulet into a strung amulet, and which may also be known as a ball of string
